OL,3,CWhat is HMS Duncan and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FThe UK is considering sending a
OL,7,Fwarship to the Middle East, while
OL,8,FFrance reportedly plans to move air
OL,9,Fdefence systems to Cyprus after a
OL,10,FBritish base on the island was hit by
OL,11,Fa drone.
OL,13,FHMS Duncan is understood to be the
OL,14,FType 45 destroyer deployed to the
OL,15,Fregion, having just completed a recent
OL,16,Fcounter-drone operations exercise.
OL,18,FWhat is HMS Duncan and what are its
OL,19,Fcapabilities?
OL,21,FWhat is it?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
