OL,3,CWhat is HMS Duncan and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FThe HMS Duncan is one of the most
OL,7,Fadvanced warships in the world,
OL,8,Faccording to the Royal Navy.
OL,10,FIt is one of six Type 45 air defence
OL,11,Fdestroyers, known as the Daring class,
OL,12,Fwhich were purpose-built for anti-
OL,13,Faircraft and anti-missile warfare.
OL,15,FSpanning 152 metres in length, it is
OL,16,Fmanned by more than 200 personnel and
OL,17,Fis currently based at Portsmouth Naval
OL,18,FBase.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772575870
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Duncan and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FDespite the name 'destroyer', the ship
OL,7,Fis built for a range of missions from
OL,8,Fcombating pirates and defending
OL,9,Fagainst air attacks, to delivering
OL,10,Fhumanitarian aid.
OL,12,FWhat capabilities does it have?
OL,14,FAll six of the UK's Type 45 destroyers
OL,15,Ffeature:
OL,17,FA missile system known as Sea Viper,
OL,18,Fwhich is "designed to track, target
OL,19,Fand destroy a variety of high-level
OL,20,Fair threats", including cruise
OL,21,Fmissiles, fighter jets and drones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
