OL,3,CWhat is HMS Duncan and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FWhat conflicts has the HMS Duncan been
OL,7,Finvolved in?
OL,9,FThe HMS Duncan's history goes back to
OL,10,F1805, when the First Duncan was built
OL,11,Fin what was then Bombay, now Mumbai,
OL,12,Ffor the East India Company, and
OL,13,Fclassed as a fifth-rate 38-gun frigate.
OL,15,FThe ship is now in its seventh
OL,16,Fiteration, which began construction by
OL,17,FBAE Systems in January 2007 and
OL,18,Flaunched on October 11, 2010.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
