PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772575870
OL,3,CWhat is HMS Duncan and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FIt began its maiden deployment in
OL,7,FMarch 2017, setting off from
OL,8,FPortsmouth and spending nine months in
OL,9,Fthe Mediterranean, Middle East and
OL,10,FGulf "working with allies... to
OL,11,Fprotect allied and merchant shipping
OL,12,Fand wider British interests in the
OL,13,Fregion".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
