OL,3,CWhat is HMS Duncan and what are its
OL,4,Ccapabilities?
OL,6,FPrevious incarnations of the ship
OL,7,Fbombarded submarine bases off Belgium
OL,8,Fin the First World War, helped sink
OL,9,Ffive U-boats in the Second World War,
OL,10,Fand was awarded the Freedom of the
OL,11,FCity of Hull for its service during
OL,12,Fthe Cod Wars (a series of disputes
OL,13,Fbetween Britain and Iceland over
OL,14,Ffishing 1950s and 70s).
OL,16,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,17,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,18,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,19,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
